<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 07 at 6:36AM EST  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Slick Travel Possible This Morning...
Periods of light snow, combined with temperatures near freezing,
may cause a thin layer of snow to accumulate on untreated or
infrequently traveled roads this morning. Reduce your speeds and
give yourself more braking time when stopping.</description>
